description:
Welcome to a special (10 Part) interview mini series with Verdine White, the bass player from Earth, Wind, and Fire.  Verdine goes one-on-one with interviewer Bob Barboza from Kids Talk Radio and Super School Teen TV.  They talk about Verdines experience with Earth, Wind, and Fire, high school days, going to the White House and much more. Verdine talks about his experiences with Michael Jackson and going to Michael's memorial service.  Verdine has a youth foundation and kids get music lesson.  We took photos of Verdine at home and competed an audio podcast for Kids Talk Radio.

All (10) videos are posted on our Kids Talk Radio You Tube site.

In addition, you can find both video and audio podcasts, and photos of Verdine at home in Los Angeles.  For more information visit: www.KidsTalkRadioLA.com
Or our new Apple Site: http://web.me.com/bobbarboza2/KidsTalkRadio/Welcome.html

E-Mail: Suprschool@aol.com
